# LLVM Obfuscation Plugin Notice

This directory contains LLVM obfuscation pass plugins built from the LLVM project.

## Origin

These plugins are built from LLVM source code with custom obfuscation passes:
- Source: https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project
- Obfuscation passes based on OLLVM (Obfuscator-LLVM)
- Custom modifications for modern LLVM compatibility

## License

Apache License 2.0 with LLVM Exceptions

See LICENSE file for full license text.

## Modifications

The following obfuscation passes have been integrated:
1. **Control Flow Flattening** - Converts control flow into switch-based state machines
2. **Instruction Substitution** - Replaces instructions with complex equivalent sequences
3. **Bogus Control Flow** - Inserts fake branches and unreachable code
4. **Basic Block Splitting** - Splits basic blocks to increase complexity

All passes have been ported to LLVM 19.x and modernized for the new pass manager.

